To install this on your own system, paste the following into the Terminal. 

Mac, Linux, Unix
git clone https://github.com/fuxy/My-Vim-Repo ~/.vim
ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Windows
git clone https://github.com/fuxy/My-Vim-Repo ~/vimfiles
ln -s ~/vimfiles/vimrc ~/_vimrc

...That's it. Let me know if you have any questions!
